comments: Mitchell (UTA) briefly has his arms around Poeltl's (SAS) upper half before quickly sliding them off.
Murray (SAS) rests his hand on Conley's (UTA) left hip and quickly releases as they move over the screen.
Gobert (UTA) firms up in his screening position in Murray's (SAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Mitchell (UTA) grabs and pulls Poeltl's (SAS) shorts, affecting Poeltl's SQBR as the pass into the post is made.
Poeltl (SAS) firms up in his screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact.
Gobert (UTA) brings his right forearm forward toward Poeltl's (SAS) front and marginal contact occurs after the release of the floater attempt.
Gobert (UTA) brushes Poeltl's (SAS) front and marginal contact occurs during the put-back attempt.
Murray (SAS) briefly has his arm around Conley's (UTA) upper half and corrects as the screen approaches.
White (SAS) moves alongside of Mitchell's (UTA) path to the basket and makes marginal contact that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) brings his off arm toward O'Neale (UTA) and marginal contact occurs with O'Neale's front and left arm as he applies the on-ball pressure.
Poeltl (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact, some of which occurs to Mitchell's leg.
Mitchell (UTA) maintains a rested forearm on White's (SAS) front and marginal contact occurs as White drives toward the free throw line.
Poeltl (SAS) turns alongside Mitchell's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs as Mitchell drives into the lane.
Poeltl (SAS) brushes Mitchell's (UTA) right shoulder and marginal contact occurs after the start of Mitchell's upward shooting motion.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of basket interference was overturned and the successful field goal by Mitchell (UTA) was counted.
Poeltl (SAS) firms up in his screening position in Conley's (UTA) front and absorbs the contact.
Gobert (UTA) extends and delivers body contact to Walker IV (SAS) during the driving shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) and White (SAS) legally contest Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
The ball rolls out of the imaginary cylinder above the rim before Murray (SAS) makes contact with it.
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Murray (SAS).
Johnson (SAS) extends for the rebound and makes contact with the part of Gobert's (UTA) hand that is on the ball.
Walker IV (SAS) and Mitchell (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Poeltl (SAS) cleanly blocks Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt before any incidental contact occurs. White (SAS) legally contests Mitchell's jump shot attempt.
